msgid "<em>Add the description of this dish here.</em>"
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_bistro
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bistro.s_text_block
msgid ""
"A healthy kitchen with local products. We’re constantly looking to propose "
"new products and receipts. <b>While respecting seasons' products and "
"nature.</b>"
msgstr ""
"ເຮືອນຄົວເພື່ອສຸຂະພາບດ້ວຍຜະລິດຕະພັນທ້ອງຖິ່ນ. ພວກເຮົາຊອກຫາຜະລິດຕະພັນ ແລະ ສູດອາຫານໃໝ່ໆຢູ່ສະເໝີ. <b>"
"ໂດຍໃຫ້ຄວາມສຳຄັນກັບຜະລິດຕະພັນຕາມລະດູການ ແລະ ທຳມະຊາດ.</b>"

#. module: theme_bistro
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bistro.s_quotes_carousel
msgid ""
"A truly exquisite dining experience. I highly recommend the Mustard Sauce, "
"out of this world."
msgstr ""
"ປະສົບການການຮັບປະທານອາຫານທີ່ດີເລີດແທ້ໆ. ຂ້ອຍຂໍແນະນຳ ຊອດມັດສະຕາດ (Mustard Sauce), ມັນແຊບແບ"
"ບບໍ່ມີບ່ອນຕິເລີຍ."

#. module: theme_bistro
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bistro.s_text_block
msgid ""
"At the Bistro, you can expect a healthy kitchen on a daily basis. <br/>Come "
"and visit us for a Sunday brunch, healthy juices full of nutrition, or "
"delicious cakes that satisfy your sweet tooth. <b>And each day, you’ll "
"discover our Today’s Special.</b>"
msgstr ""
"ທີ່ Bistro, ທ່ານຈະໄດ້ພົບກັບອາຫານເພື່ອສຸຂະພາບໃນທຸກໆມື້. <br/>ມາຢ້ຽມຢາມພວກເຮົາສຳລັບ ອາຫານເຊົ້າຄວ"
"ບສວາຍໃນວັນອາທິດ, ນ້ຳຜັກຜົນໄມ້ເພື່ອສຸຂະພາບທີ່ເຕັມໄປດ້ວຍຄຸນຄ່າທາງໂພຊະນາການ, ຫຼື ເຄັກທີ່ແຊບຊ້ອຍສຳລັບຄົນ"
"ຮັກຂອງຫວານ. <b>ແລະ ໃນແຕ່ລະມື້, ທ່ານຈະໄດ້ພົບກັບ ເມນູພິເສດປະຈຳວັນ ຂອງພວກເຮົາ.</b>"

#. module: theme_bistro
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bistro.s_features
msgid "Breakfast"
msgstr "ອາຫານເຊົ້າ"

#. module: theme_bistro
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bistro.s_quotes_carousel
msgid ""
"Cosy and friendly, good atmosphere and super food. Especially the spiced "
"fruit crumble."
msgstr ""
"ອົບອຸ່ນ ແລະ ເປັນກັນເອງ, ບັນຍາກາດດີ ແລະ ອາຫານດີຫຼາຍ. ໂດຍສະເພາະແມ່ນ fruit crumble ທີ່ໃສ່ເຄື່ອງ"
"ເທດ."

#. module: theme_bistro
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bistro.s_cover
msgid ""
"Daily fresh products combined with our professional yet convivial "
"service<br/> to create a true gastronomic experience."
msgstr ""
"ຜະລິດຕະພັນທີ່ສົດໃໝ່ທຸກມື້ ປະສົມປະສານກັບການບໍລິການແບບມືອາຊີບແຕ່ເປັນກັນເອງ <br/> ເພື່ອສ້າງປະສົບການດ້ານ"
"ອາຫານທີ່ແທ້ຈິງ."

#. module: theme_bistro
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bistro.s_features
msgid "Dinner"
msgstr "ອາຫານແລງ"

#. module: theme_bistro
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bistro.s_features
msgid ""
"Enjoy tasty food with friends.<br/><small>From <b>6:30 pm</b> to <b>10:30 "
"pm</b></small>"
msgstr ""
"ເພີດເພີນກັບອາຫານທີ່ແຊບຊ້ອຍກັບໝູ່ເພື່ອນ.<br/><small>ຕັ້ງແຕ່ <b>18:30</b> ຫາ <b>22:30</b></"
"small>"

#. module: theme_bistro
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bistro.s_features
msgid ""
"Help you start your morning right.<br/><small>From <b>7:30 am</b> to "
"<b>10:30 am</b></small>"
msgstr ""
"ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຕອນເຊົ້າຢ່າງຖືກຕ້ອງ.<br/><small>ຕັ້ງແຕ່ <b>7:30</b> ຫາ <b>10:30</b></"
"small>"

#. module: theme_bistro
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bistro.s_features
msgid "Lunch"
msgstr "ອາຫານທ່ຽງ"

#. module: theme_bistro
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bistro.s_cover
msgid "Our Menu"
msgstr "ເມນູຂອງພວກເຮົາ"

#. module: theme_bistro
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bistro.s_cover
msgid "Seasonal<br/> Flavors"
msgstr "ລົດຊາດ<br/> ຕາມລະດູການ"

#. module: theme_bistro
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bistro.s_features
msgid ""
"Take a break from your busy schedule.<br/><small>From <b>11:30 am</b> to "
"<b>2:30 pm</b></small>"
msgstr ""
"ພັກຜ່ອນຈາກຕາຕະລາງທີ່ຫຍຸ້ງຍາກຂອງທ່ານ.<br/><small>ຕັ້ງແຕ່ <b>11:30</b> ຫາ <b>14:30</b></"
"small>"

#. module: theme_bistro
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bistro.s_picture
msgid ""
"Taste our chef's special, an almond macaroon with orange blossom "
"buttercream."
msgstr ""
"ຊີມເມນູພິເສດຈາກພໍ່ຄົວຂອງພວກເຮົາ, ມາຄາຣອນອັນມອນ ພ້ອມກັບຄຣີມບັດເຕີກິ່ນດອກສົ້ມ."

#. module: theme_bistro
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bistro.s_banner
msgid "Tasty Meals"
msgstr "ອາຫານທີ່ແຊບຊ້ອຍ"

#. module: theme_bistro
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bistro.s_picture
msgid "The perfect dessert to share for the table."
msgstr "ຂອງຫວານທີ່ສົມບູນແບບສຳລັບແບ່ງປັນກັນຢູ່ໂຕະ."

#. module: theme_bistro
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_bistro.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "ເຄື່ອງມືຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອຂອງທີມ (Theme Utils)"

#. module: theme_bistro
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bistro.s_quotes_carousel
msgid "This place is perfect for groups or a casual date night."
msgstr "ສະຖານທີ່ນີ້ເໝາະສຳລັບການມາເປັນກຸ່ມ ຫຼື ການເດດແບບສະບາຍໆ."

#. module: theme_bistro
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bistro.s_picture
msgid "Today's special"
msgstr "ເມນູພິເສດມື້ນີ້"
